  <scopecontent id="9433070929e94061fbf336c393794866">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>Mary Loftus served as the Manager of Information Dissemination and Administration in the Office of Communications at the Ford Foundation. This collection is composed of her office files, including correspondence, annual report draft files, and files related to the creation of the Ford Foundation's early website. The bulk of the material in the collection spans from 1995-1999.</p>  </scopecontent>
